Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory54.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: 'Gabriel, do you think Miss Luna has been acting quite strange recently?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "She's even appearing on the battlefield.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: "Our leader appearing on the battlefield boosts troop morale. It shouldn't be considered strange.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Forget it...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'With that, Roland picks up a stone and chucks it at a tree behind him.'}
{3: 'The stone, however, does not connect with the tree. Instead, it stops midair.'}
{3: 'Then, slowly, a hand grows out of the stone, slowly corporealizing into a body. Arm, torso, until the figure reveals itself coiling around the tree with several legs.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lamia', 3: "Eeek...! Watch out! Why'd you throw at me!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Reminds me, can she really handle it all by herself?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: "I-I guess...? She said we don't have to provide her with any support. We can just withdraw once we complete our mission...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "...Sounds like something she'd say.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "You spend more time with Miss Luna than we do, don't you find it a bit off?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'N-no, not really... But I guess Miss Luna has been spending more time by herself than usual...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "And you still don't find it strange, huh...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'B-but Miss Luna and Miss Alpha are just the same as ever...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "...Oh, you're just—Sigh.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'I had you keep an eye on "her." Any news?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: "Uh, well... You got nothing with a direct confrontation. What makes you think I'd have any updates...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: '..."She" seems to be traveling aimlessly as usual.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "...That's the dog that didn't bark, dear Watson.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Based on the signal we recently sent out in South America, "she" seems to be acting as if nothing happened.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: "Maybe she didn't catch the news.", 4: '3'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'As you know, ground relay is slower than it used to be.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "Is there any possibility... that we've all been gravely mistaken?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'What if "she" doesn\'t really care?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'If so, then "she" is by no means a good agent.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Who stipulated that an agent must be loyal to their duty? Do you even know how agents are created?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "Look, even WE don't know. Non-agents know nothing about agents.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "That's the issue.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Roland is about to continue, when Lamia points off into the distance.'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: "I-it's beginning...", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Roland and Gabriel look to where Lamia is pointing and see the Arctic Route Union surrounded by an explosion of fire and smoke.'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "What's going on...? Wouldn't forcing them away achieve her goal already?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'Miss Luna... is trying to bring destruction upon them all.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "This does not bode well. We've revealed our hand too early...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'All while Babylonia and "she" still have their hands covered, we\'re forced to be on the passive.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Let us wait and consult with Miss Luna when she returns. Perhaps we no longer need to lurk in the dark.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Maybe, just maybe...', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory39.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: '‘421’', 3: 'So, are you still going to side with them?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Shadows outstretched, the room is bathed in darkness. The robot looks over at a mysterious figure standing half-illuminated before it.'}
{3: 'The shadowy figure lights a fire, leaving a fiery dot in the darkness, trailing with a puff of white smoke.'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Indeed. This is all quite amusing.'}
{2: '???', 3: 'And with the addition of Huaxu, this has become... all the more interesting.'}
{2: '‘421’', 3: "If only I hadn't spared your life.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: "I'd say the same thing if I were you."}
{2: '???', 3: "I'm sure me being alive has been quite the thorn in your side."}
{2: '‘421’', 3: "But as you know, I've never really cared about it. You're still of use to me now.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Useful to you? Or do you mean the two old guys above you?'}
{2: '‘421’', 3: "You know I can't answer you that.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Never expected you to anyways.'}
{2: '???', 3: 'What information do you have in exchange?'}
{2: '‘421’', 3: "Enough intel to keep you away from the tip of Babylonia's spear in the coming days.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Fair enough. Let me ask you this... What purpose does "Huaxu" serve?'}
{2: '‘421’', 3: '"Huaxu" is an AI. As for its purpose, that is for its owner to decide.', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: "You're right. My point is, Huaxu may have a new master, but has her master... really changed?"}
{3: 'The shadowy figure shakes their head and nods. The mechanical joints in their hands clench and loose. Finally, a few chuckles slide out of the speaker.'}
{2: '‘421’', 3: 'Last question—how big of a piece do you want of the pie?', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Who said I only wanted a piece? What if—I want the whole pie?'}
{2: '‘421’', 3: 'You can certainly try...', 4: '1'}
